<h1 id="manage-employee-leave" sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-manage-employee-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="33">Manage employee leave</h1>

<p sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-manage-employee-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="35">You can manage an employee's leave by leave type. This includes expiring leave enrollment and adjusting leave type balances.</p>
