<li sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-manage-employee-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="41"><p sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-manage-employee-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="41">Select <strong sourcefile="articles/human-resources/hr-leave-and-absence-manage-employee-leave.md" sourcestartlinenumber="41">Leave and absence setup</strong>.</p>
